Package com.oracle.tools.runtime.console

Class Summary
ErrorApplicationConsole A ErrorApplicationConsole is an implementation of an ApplicationConsole.
FileWriterApplicationConsole A FileWriterApplicationConsole is an implementation of an ApplicationConsole that logs output to a file.
NullApplicationConsole A NullApplicationConsole is an implementation of an ApplicationConsole that silently ignores attempts to output.
PrintStreamApplicationConsole A PrintStreamApplicationConsole is an ApplicationConsole that writes to a PrintStream.
SystemApplicationConsole A SystemApplicationConsole is an implementation of an ApplicationConsole that writes output to the System.out.
